---
import Section from './Section.astro';
---

<Section id="experience" number="02" eyebrow="Experience" heading="Where I work">
  <div
    class="relative max-w-2xl overflow-hidden rounded-lg border border-line bg-surface p-6 sm:p-8 transition-colors duration-(--duration-base) hover:border-accent/40"
  >
    <div
      class="pointer-events-none absolute -right-20 -top-20 size-52 rounded-full opacity-20"
      style="background: radial-gradient(circle, var(--color-accent), transparent 70%);"
      aria-hidden="true"
    >
    </div>
    <div class="mb-4 flex flex-wrap items-baseline justify-between gap-2">
      <h3 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold">Principal Security Analyst</h3>
      <p class="font-mono text-xs text-accent-bright">Critical Start</p>
    </div>
    <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-muted-fg">
      <li class="flex gap-3">
        <span class="mt-2 size-1 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-accent" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        Investigate security incidents and execute remediation actions on live
        threats across 2,500+ multi-tenant customer environments
      </li>
      <li class="flex gap-3">
        <span class="mt-2 size-1 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-accent" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        Work daily across multiple SIEM and EDR/XDR platforms, including
        Microsoft Defender and Sentinel, CrowdStrike Falcon, Cortex XDR/XSIAM,
        SentinelOne, and Splunk
      </li>
      <li class="flex gap-3">
        <span class="mt-2 size-1 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-accent" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        KQL-driven log analysis and detection tuning to cut alert noise at
        scale without losing signal
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</Section>
